ISLAMABAD, Mar 2 (APP): Prime Minister Imran Khan on Wednesday said robust revenue growth of 28.5 percent by the Federal Bureau of Revenue (FBR) had enabled the government to subsidize petrol and electricity.
“Because of this performance of FBR we are able to subsidize petrol, diesel, and electricity and give relief to our people,” he said in a tweet.
